com.pizza.CMModel

Class SpeiseEintrag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pizza.CMModel.DBConnect
      • com.pizza.CMModel.SpeiseEintrag

  • public class SpeiseEintrag
extends DBConnect

    Models the Speise Entry of the Speise Table

    The SpeiseEintrag class is used to model the Speise Table of the database. In addition to getters and setter of the corresponding fields, there is a method used to store a new entry to the table.
